<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The transferor's rights and obligations arising from a contract of employment or from an employment relationship existing on the date of a transfer shall, by reason of such transfer, be transferred to the transferee. </inglise>
<eesti> V&otilde;&otilde;randaja t&ouml;&ouml;lepingust v&otilde;i t&ouml;&ouml;suhtest tulenevad &otilde;igused ja kohustused, mis kehtivad &uuml;lemineku kuup&auml;eval, l&auml;hevad sellise &uuml;lemineku tagaj&auml;rjel &uuml;le omandajale. </eesti>
<inglise> Member States may provide that, after the date of transfer, the transferor and the transferee shall be jointly and severally liable in respect of obligations which arose before the date of transfer from a contract of employment or an employment relationship existing on the date of the transfer. </inglise>
<eesti> Liikmesriigid v&otilde;ivad n&auml;ha ette, et p&auml;rast &uuml;lemineku kuup&auml;eva vastutavad v&otilde;&otilde;randaja ja omandaja solidaarselt kohustuste eest, mis tulenevad &uuml;lemineku kuup&auml;eval kehtivast t&ouml;&ouml;lepingust v&otilde;i -suhtest enne &uuml;lemineku kuup&auml;eva. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Member States may adopt appropriate measures to ensure that the transferor notifies the transferee of all the rights and obligations which will be transferred to the transferee under this Article, so far as those rights and obligations are or ought to have been known to the transferor at the time of the transfer. </inglise>
<eesti> Liikmesriigid v&otilde;ivad v&otilde;tta asjakohaseid meetmeid tagamaks, et v&otilde;&otilde;randaja teataks omandajale k&otilde;ikidest k&auml;esoleva artikli kohaselt omandajale &uuml;leminevatest &otilde;igustest ja kohustustest, niiv&otilde;rd kuiv&otilde;rd v&otilde;&otilde;randaja &uuml;lemineku ajal nendest teadlik on v&otilde;i olema peaks. </eesti>
<inglise> A failure by the transferor to notify the transferee of any such right or obligation shall not affect the transfer of that right or obligation and the rights of any employees against the transferee and/or transferor in respect of that right or obligation. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui v&otilde;&otilde;randaja j&auml;tab omandajale sellisest &otilde;igusest v&otilde;i kohustusest teatamata, ei m&otilde;juta see sellise &otilde;iguse v&otilde;i kohustuse &uuml;leminekut ega t&ouml;&ouml;tajate &otilde;igusi omandaja ja/v&otilde;i v&otilde;&otilde;randaja suhtes seoses k&otilde;nealuse &otilde;iguse v&otilde;i kohustusega. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> Following the transfer, the transferee shall continue to observe the terms and conditions agreed in any collective agreement on the same terms applicable to the transferor under that agreement, until the date of termination or expiry of the collective agreement or the entry into force or application of another collective agreement. </inglise>
