<inglise> Article 5 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 5 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> If the undertaking, business or part of an undertaking or business preserves its autonomy, the status and function of the representatives or of the representation of the employees affected by the transfer shall be preserved on the same terms and subject to the same conditions as existed before the date of the transfer by virtue of law, regulation, administrative provision or agreement, provided that the conditions necessary for the constitution of the employees' representation are fulfilled. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui ettev&otilde;te, &auml;ri&uuml;hing v&otilde;i ettev&otilde;tte v&otilde;i &auml;ri&uuml;hingu osa s&auml;ilitab oma iseseisvuse, s&auml;ilivad &uuml;leminekust m&otilde;jutatud t&ouml;&ouml;tajate esindajate v&otilde;i esinduskogu seisund ja funktsioon samadel tingimustel nagu need, mis kehtisid vastavalt &otilde;igus- ja haldusnormidele v&otilde;i kokkulepetele enne &uuml;lemineku kuup&auml;eva, kui on t&auml;idetud t&ouml;&ouml;tajate esinduskogu moodustamiseks vajalikud tingimused. </eesti>
<inglise> The first subparagraph shall not apply if, under the laws, regulations, administrative provisions or practice in the Member States, or by agreement with the representatives of the employees, the conditions necessary for the reappointment of the representatives of the employees or for the reconstitution of the representation of the employees are fulfilled. </inglise>
<eesti> Esimest l&otilde;iku ei kohaldata, kui liikmesriikide &otilde;igus- ja haldusnormide v&otilde;i tavade v&otilde;i t&ouml;&ouml;tajate esindajatega s&otilde;lmitud kokkuleppe kohaselt on t&auml;idetud tingimused t&ouml;&ouml;tajate esindajate tagasinimetamiseks v&otilde;i t&ouml;&ouml;tajate esinduskogu taastamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise> Where the transferor is the subject of bankruptcy proceedings or any analogous insolvency proceedings which have been instituted with a view to the liquidation of the assets of the transferor and are under the supervision of a competent public authority (which may be an insolvency practitioner authorised by a competent public authority), Member States may take the necessary measures to ensure that the transferred employees are properly represented until the new election or designation of representatives of the employees. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui v&otilde;&otilde;randaja vastu on algatatud pankrotimenetlus v&otilde;i analoogiline maksej&otilde;uetusmenetlus v&otilde;&otilde;randaja varade likvideerimiseks, mis toimub p&auml;deva asutuse j&auml;relevalve all (kelleks v&otilde;ib olla p&auml;deva asutuse m&auml;&auml;ratud pankrotihaldur), v&otilde;ivad liikmesriigid v&otilde;tta vajalikke meetmeid, et tagada &uuml;leviidud t&ouml;&ouml;tajate n&otilde;uetekohane esindatus kuni t&ouml;&ouml;tajate esindajate uue valimise v&otilde;i nimetamiseni. </eesti>
<inglise> If the undertaking, business or part of an undertaking or business does not preserve its autonomy, the Member States shall take the necessary measures to ensure that the employees transferred who were represented before the transfer continue to be properly represented during the period necessary for the reconstitution or reappointment of the representation of employees in accordance with national law or practice. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui ettev&otilde;te, &auml;ri&uuml;hing v&otilde;i ettev&otilde;tte v&otilde;i &auml;ri&uuml;hingu osa oma iseseisvust ei s&auml;ilita, v&otilde;tavad liikmesriigid vajalikud meetmed, et tagada &uuml;leviidud t&ouml;&ouml;tajate, kellel enne &uuml;leviimist olid esindajad, j&auml;tkuv n&otilde;uetekohane esindatus ajavahemiku jooksul, mis on vajalik t&ouml;&ouml;tajate esinduskogu taastamiseks v&otilde;i tagasinimetamiseks vastavalt siseriiklikule &otilde;igusele v&otilde;i tavale. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> If the term of office of the representatives of the employees affected by the transfer expires as a result of the transfer, the representatives shall continue to enjoy the protection provided by the laws, regulations, administrative provisions or practice of the Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui &uuml;leminekust m&otilde;jutatud t&ouml;&ouml;tajate esindajate ametiaeg l&otilde;peb &uuml;lemineku tulemusena, j&auml;tkub esindajate kaitse koosk&otilde;las liikmesriikide &otilde;igus- ja haldusnormidega v&otilde;i tavadega. </eesti>
