<inglise> Article 7 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 7 </eesti>
<inglise> This Directive shall not affect the right of Member States to apply or introduce laws, regulations or administrative provisions which are more favourable to employees or to promote or permit collective agreements or agreements between social partners more favourable to employees. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev direktiiv ei piira liikmesriikide &otilde;igust kohaldada v&otilde;i vastu v&otilde;tta &otilde;igus- ja haldusnorme, mis on t&ouml;&ouml;tajate jaoks soodsamad, v&otilde;i soodustada v&otilde;i lubada t&ouml;&ouml;tajate jaoks soodsamaid kollektiivlepinguid v&otilde;i sotsiaalpartnerite vahelisi kokkuleppeid. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 7a </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 7a </eesti>
<inglise> Member States shall introduce into their national legal systems such measures as are necessary to enable all employees and representatives of employees who consider themselves wronged by failure to comply with the obligations arising from this Directive to pursue their claims by judicial process after possible recourse to other competent authorities. </inglise>
<eesti> Liikmesriigid v&otilde;tavad oma siseriiklikus &otilde;iguss&uuml;steemis meetmed v&otilde;imaldamaks t&ouml;&ouml;tajatel ja t&ouml;&ouml;tajate esindajatel, kes leiavad, et neid on k&auml;esolevas direktiivis s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uete eiramise t&otilde;ttu &otilde;igusvastaselt koheldud, taotleda oma &otilde;iguste kaitset kohtu kaudu, olles vastava v&otilde;imaluse korral esmalt p&ouml;&ouml;rdunud p&auml;devate asutuste poole. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 7b </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 7b </eesti>
<inglise> The Commission shall submit to the Council an analysis of the effects of the provisions of this Directive before 17 July 2006. </inglise>
<eesti> Komisjon esitab n&otilde;ukogule anal&uuml;&uuml;si k&auml;esoleva direktiivi s&auml;tete toime kohta enne 17. juulit 2006. </eesti>
<inglise> It shall propose any amendment which may seem necessary. </inglise>
<eesti> Komisjon teeb vajaduse korral muudatusettepanekuid. </eesti>
